cast.overview: An investigator from the War Crimes Commission travels to Connecticut to find an infamous Nazi, who may be hiding out in a small town in the guise of a distinguished professor engaged to the Supreme Court Justice’s daughter.
cast.title: The Stranger

details.biography: Isabel O'Madigan was born on 16 October 1871 in St. Louis, Missouri, USA. She was an actress, known for Bab's Diary (1917), The Egg and I (1947) and Bab's Matinee Idol (1917). She died on 23 January 1951 in Culver City, Los Angeles, California, USA.
details.name: Isabel O'Madigan
